Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.77,0:00:55.13,OP,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.13,0:00:59.14,OP,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.14,0:01:03.96,OP,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.70,0:01:11.78,OP,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:18.93,OP,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.23,0:01:25.55,OP,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.94,0:01:33.21,OP,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.75,0:01:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted you to move on with your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.26,0:01:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You embarrassed a lot of the council members back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.64,0:01:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,They won't just let Chor Tempest carry on as it did before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.94,0:02:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,While {\i1}Arcus Prima{\i0} is being repaired, Chor Tempest will be stationed aboard the {\i1}Messis{\i0}.  
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.89,0:02:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You will fly patrols and reconnaissance missions near the border.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.97,0:02:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait... you mean we're actually going to fly on {\i1}that{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.39,0:02:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.96,0:02:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get greedy. We're lucky they're letting Chor Tempest survive at all. 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.94,0:02:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.43,0:02:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's great. Even the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not complaining at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.36,0:02:49.37,Series,,0,0,0,,Birds in a Cage
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.53,0:03:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we really have to all live in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.38,0:03:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Floe, instead of complaining, you should hurry up and choose your bunk. 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.96,0:03:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The beds by the window are first-come, first-served.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.05,0:03:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.63,0:03:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we're neighbours, Floe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.49,0:03:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Howdy, Aaeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.10,0:03:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Nee-san, are we going to be staying here permanently?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.18,0:03:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we can't change what's already happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.68,0:03:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and we don't know what may happen tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.02,0:03:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.37,0:04:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaimu is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.21,0:04:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yun, where's Mamiina?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.33,0:04:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.76,0:04:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.31,0:04:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It must have happened during transport.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The speaker cable mechanism is loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.31,0:04:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you fix it somehow without replacing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.62,0:04:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'll find a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.73,0:04:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, parts are going to be harder to get.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.87,0:04:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.16,0:04:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.82,0:04:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems pretty tough, Wapourif.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.62,0:04:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,For the sibyllae, who come from such a high-class background, 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.25,0:04:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a lot about this ship that will be a rude awakening. 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.23,0:04:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,"High-class," eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.32,0:04:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess this isn't the time to worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.39,0:04:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, as for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.96,0:04:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,"...as long as I can fly Simoun." Right? 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.20,0:05:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.05,0:05:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So that is how patrol duty will be divided.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.69,0:05:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.55,0:05:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Sibylla Dominura...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.15,0:05:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.99,0:05:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Chor Tempest is the best choir in the entire Simulacrum Theocracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.84,0:05:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the ultimate honour for me and my crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.31,0:05:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But why are you going to the front in an old rust bucket like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.99,0:05:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain, the look on your face says "this is all such a bother."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.11,0:05:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.34,0:05:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's understandable. You're quite correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.10,0:05:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially since someone like me, from another command, will be coming onto your bridge. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.00,0:05:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand, Sibylla Dominura.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.61,0:05:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't bother you with any more questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.85,0:06:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sibylla, please stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.91,0:06:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sibylla, this is beneath you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.28,0:06:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.12,0:06:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I've worked in the kitchen since I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.95,0:06:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm having fun doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.71,0:07:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We're approaching the border with Argentum.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.31,0:07:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There have been a lot of incursions around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.02,0:07:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though this is just a routine patrol mission,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.94,0:07:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,don't let your guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.63,0:07:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A "routine patrol mission," eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.73,0:07:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.60,0:07:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,"When Simoun sibyllae fly, they are praying to the sky." 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.08,0:07:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And flying in a Simoun is "speaking to the Simoun."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.17,0:07:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,True. We speak with the Simoun so we can pray to the sky. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Para-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.10,0:07:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We're scheduled to return at noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.17,0:07:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.92,0:07:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyaaa!!! A mouse! THERE'S A MOUSE!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.31,0:07:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Where? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.66,0:07:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.25,0:07:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A mouse? Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.44,0:07:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you afraid of it, Aaeru?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.65,0:07:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a country girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.94,0:07:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We had lots of mice down on the farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.94,0:07:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, didn't you have them too, Mamiina?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.22,0:08:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Two o'clock low!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.47,0:08:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,They're a long way off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.33,0:08:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the third time we've seen them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, those guys are just annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.67,0:08:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Para-sama, we should go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.11,0:08:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. They're too far away to go after.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.81,0:08:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll go back and report.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.32,0:08:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't stand having to live in that room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.59,0:08:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does Dominura get special treatment?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.18,0:08:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's fishy here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.20,0:08:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Dominura who got us this ship. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.55,0:08:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't say such things about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.63,0:08:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.95,0:08:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sick and tired of listening to you complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.18,0:09:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaeru, don't mice bite people?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.31,0:09:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Only when they're hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.85,0:09:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They do bite!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.06,0:09:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work. How did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.86,0:09:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We spotted a few Argentine patrols, off in the distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.89,0:09:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But they ran away as soon as they saw us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.82,0:09:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.78,0:09:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't feel right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.71,0:09:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,They were quite far off, and they disappeared at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.66,0:09:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me your report.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.64,0:10:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, the acting captain graces us with her illustrious presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.93,0:10:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,My position is as I explained.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.54,0:10:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall I go over it again, Kaimu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.39,0:10:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Neviril is Chor Tempest's Regina.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.18,0:10:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Dominura is acting as a liaison between us and Captain Wauf of the {\i1}Messis{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.03,0:10:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And she's also a member of Chor Tempest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.18,0:10:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Paraietta. Give your report to Dominura.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.50,0:10:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Lunchtime, everyone! Lunchtime!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.57,0:10:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Mamiina made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.39,0:10:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You look lonely, Guragief.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.83,0:10:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's it exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.53,0:10:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Very lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.45,0:11:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Anubituf, I thought you felt the same. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.41,0:11:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.20,0:11:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Chor Tempest are glorious Simoun sibyllae.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.46,0:11:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But... we snatched their glory away from them. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.17,0:11:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever it takes, I will try to help them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.14,0:11:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I will, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.24,0:11:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do everything I can to get them transferred back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.81,0:11:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.88,0:11:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But whether it would be in their best interest to bring them back to the {\i1}Arcus Prima{\i0}, 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.13,0:11:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I honestly don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.82,0:11:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Itadakimasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.54,0:11:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.73,0:11:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.95,0:11:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Smells good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.79,0:11:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm seeing you in a whole new light.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.11,0:11:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.21,0:11:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nice and hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.56,0:11:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.12,0:11:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm, tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.67,0:11:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I made a lot of it, so you can all have seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.55,0:11:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.61,0:11:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Mamiina, won't you eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.69,0:12:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Itadakimasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.93,0:12:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.20,0:12:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.90,0:12:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened before...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.56,0:12:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.75,0:12:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just pretend it never happened, shall we, Mamiina?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.57,0:12:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.59,0:12:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.20,0:12:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you just tell me, Mamiina?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.02,0:12:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.66,0:12:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.07,0:12:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this seat taken?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.99,0:12:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.25,0:13:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.53,0:13:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Mamiina...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.55,0:13:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I maybe speak with you after dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.39,0:13:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.51,0:13:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The new sibylla made it, did she?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.09,0:13:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It's pretty tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.34,0:13:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mamiina?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.71,0:13:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You asked me here, and you're late, Rodoreamon. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.23,0:13:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I got lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.80,0:13:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,On such a small ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.38,0:13:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well. What do you have to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.62,0:13:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you have to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.52,0:13:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're not going to say anything—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.78,0:14:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.74,0:14:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.54,0:14:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come here, Mamiina.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.23,0:14:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, it wasn't as if I didn't feel anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.97,0:14:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What can I do to be friends with you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.35,0:14:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,"Again?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.83,0:14:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You make it sound as if we used to be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.70,0:14:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth of the matter is that one of us was always meant to be on top, and the other below.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.23,0:14:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.92,0:14:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh, what were you thinking back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.41,0:14:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to be friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.52,0:14:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop spouting nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.79,0:14:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...and I feel the same way now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.04,0:14:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing more to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.88,0:14:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I... always envied your braids.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.84,0:15:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.29,0:15:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...was the way your parents told you to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.18,0:15:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't something that a child would have understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.61,0:15:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just Her Little Ladyship's hairstyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.36,0:15:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's... not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.27,0:15:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,All the other Simoun sibyllae love and respect Chor Tempest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.46,0:15:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We're proud of them. They are the best choir of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.25,0:15:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,In the name of all of the Simoun sibyllae,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.09,0:15:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I request that Chor Tempest remain in service.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.45,0:15:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mean the Chor Tempest who act as priestesses,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.84,0:15:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,or the Chor Tempest who "fight" in "battle" as a unit?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.81,0:16:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Which Chor Tempest is it that you want us to keep?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.74,0:16:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They are twelve sibyllae who form pairs and draw Ri Maajons in the sky.  
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.52,0:16:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There can be only one Chor Tempest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.91,0:16:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Back at the hearing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.37,0:16:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You were there, too, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.39,0:16:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I heard part of the proceedings.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.19,0:16:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to Vyura and Onashia, Chor Tempest was able to survive. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.81,0:16:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Your performance was wonderful, too, Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not trying to lay blame for these days of fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.08,0:16:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It has been painful and heartbreaking, and perhaps this is fate. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.70,0:16:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It may even be the will of Tempus Spatium.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.22,0:16:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, though, I don't care what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.69,0:16:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, I don't care about "the will of God."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.38,0:16:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's she saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.17,0:16:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I just have one question I'd like to ask you all:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.02,0:17:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,In spite of that... am I still a Simoun sibylla?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.54,0:17:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So you heard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.95,0:17:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Neviril. The next patrol assignment, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.26,0:17:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You and Limone will be next, along with Alti and Flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.94,0:17:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.84,0:17:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Dominura.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You{\i0} were the one who {\i1}really{\i0} saved Chor Tempest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.56,0:17:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You got us this ship, on the condition that we would go to the front,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.33,0:17:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,by negotiating with the Council.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.31,0:17:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.59,0:17:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Chor Tempest is the Simulacrum Theocracy's best choir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.64,0:17:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Make no mistake about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.86,0:17:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But how are you able to do things like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.05,0:18:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! That's really neat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.00,0:18:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a memento from my Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.26,0:18:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Paraietta. Are you in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.40,0:18:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.73,0:18:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.06,0:18:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to talk to you again about the enemy patrols this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.90,0:18:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. What about them?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.23,0:18:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,How many times did you see the enemy in the distance,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.63,0:18:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,but have them run away immediately after?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.20,0:18:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly three times. They did the same thing each time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.17,0:18:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.58,0:18:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Did {\i1}you{\i0} really spot {\i1}them{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.66,0:19:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it actually you who saw them first?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.58,0:19:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if they spotted us first...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.31,0:19:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,then they {\i1}wanted{\i0} us to see them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.53,0:19:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.59,0:19:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Paraietta, we'd better hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.59,0:19:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go tell the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.65,0:19:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest of you, get to the flight deck right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.84,0:19:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Neviril. I didn't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.52,0:19:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,They must have followed the route of your patrol.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.01,0:19:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,They might try to ambush Dominura and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.75,0:19:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We're up on the front lines, near the border with the enemy. 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.49,0:19:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Mamiina and Rodoreamon aren't here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.95,0:19:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood. I'll fly auriga.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.48,0:19:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaimu. Be my pair, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.44,0:19:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yun, you're my sagitta.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.57,0:19:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, Morinas.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.37,0:19:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wapourif...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.84,0:19:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll send Mamiina and Rodoreamon right after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.68,0:20:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened, Sibylla Rodoreamon, Sibylla Mamiina?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.57,0:20:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone else has taken off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.90,0:20:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Mamiina, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.79,0:20:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I won't be your pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.13,0:20:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I said it before, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.74,0:20:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely not. Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.70,0:20:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.67,0:20:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.91,0:20:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing, Rodore?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.74,0:20:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you called me when we were little.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.71,0:20:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Rodoreamon...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.13,0:20:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.63,0:20:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They all might die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.07,0:20:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,At a time like this, we can't just waste time arguing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.83,0:21:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Mamiina!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.20,0:21:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Rodo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.76,0:21:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Mamiina.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.46,0:21:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to your posts and prepare for emergency landings.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.16,0:21:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.76,0:21:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you still crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.32,0:21:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We've just about reached them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.02,0:21:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.17,0:21:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.01,0:21:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always worn my hair in braids!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.84,0:21:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.97,0:22:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.44,0:22:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,With this many of the enemy... Iron Ri Maajon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.90,0:22:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That meat we had...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.88,0:22:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It was delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.21,0:22:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It was mouse.
