Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.68,0:24:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our job to take some soldiers up close to a town.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.33,0:24:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on Simoun:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.67,0:24:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,United Front.
